classes.name: static-list
classes.description: Defines the style for the base list component.

classes.name: static-list__header
classes.description: Provides the style for the header area of a list side.

classes.name: static-list__header-text
classes.description: Provides the style for the main header text of the list.

classes.name: static-list__item-count
classes.description:
Provides the style for the "(x)" suffix after the header 
label which displays the number of visible items in the list.

classes.name: static-list__select-all-text
classes.description: Provides the style for the "Select all" text.

classes.name: static-list__deselect-all-text
classes.description: Provides the style for the "Deelect all" text.

classes.name: static-list__items
classes.description: Provides the style for a list of items.

classes.name: static-list__item
classes.description: Provides the style for a single item in a list.

classes.name: static-list__item-checkmark
classes.description: Provides the style for the check icon of a selected item.

classes.name: static-list__item-label
classes.description: Provides the style for the label in a list item.

classes.name: static-list__no-filter-results-text
classes.description:
Provides the style for the message that will display inside a
list when no items pass the current filtering.

classes.name: static-list__cdk-virtual-scroll-container
classes.description: Provides the style for the virtual scroll container that will display inside a large list.

classes.name: static-list__cdk-virtual-scroll-item
classes.description: Provides the style for a single item in a virtual scroll list.

name: drag-drop-list__cdk-virtual-scroll-item
description: Provides the style for a single item in a virtual scroll list.
